" move between tabs with []
" ctrl+tab doesn't register as different from tab. ctrl+[ is esc.

nnoremap [ :bnext<CR>:redraw<CR>
nnoremap ] :bprevious<CR>:redraw<CR>

vnoremap [ :bnext<CR>:redraw<CR>
